basic_pitch_histogram - Variable in class jsymbolic2.processing.MIDIIntermediateRepresentations
A normalized histogram with bins corresponding to MIDI pitches (0 to 127).
BasicPitchHistogramFeature - Class in jsymbolic2.features
A feature exractor that finds a features array with bins corresponding to the values of the basic pitch histogram.
BasicPitchHistogramFeature() - Constructor for class jsymbolic2.features.BasicPitchHistogramFeature
Basic constructor that sets the definition and dependencies (and their offsets) of this feature.
BeatHistogramFeature - Class in jsymbolic2.features
A feature exractor that finds a feature array with entries corresponding to the frequency values of each of the bins of the beat histogram (except the first 40 empty ones).
BeatHistogramFeature() - Constructor for class jsymbolic2.features.BeatHistogramFeature
Basic constructor that sets the definition and dependencies (and their offsets) of this feature.
BrassFractionFeature - Class in jsymbolic2.features
A feature exractor that extracts the fraction of all Note Ons belonging to brass patches (General MIDI patches 57 or 68).
BrassFractionFeature() - Constructor for class jsymbolic2.features.BrassFractionFeature
Basic constructor that sets the definition and dependencies (and their offsets) of this feature.
